	ftxfont_default_fid.
	(ftxfont_prepare_face): Use ftxfont_create_gcs to create GCs.
	(ftxfont_done_face): Free only GCs that are created by
	ftxfont_create_gcs.
	(ftxfont_draw): If face->gc != s->gc, create proper GCs.

