	Turn integer fields into `int'.  Merge x_window_low and x_window_high.
	(SCROLL_BAR_PACK, SCROLL_BAR_UNPACK, SCROLL_BAR_X_WINDOW)
	(SET_SCROLL_BAR_X_WINDOW): Remove.
