2007-08-06  YAMAMOTO Mitsuharu  <mituharu@math.s.chiba-u.ac.jp>

	* mac.c [TARGET_API_MAC_CARBON] (cfdate_to_lisp): Obtain microsec value.
	Use kCFAbsoluteTimeIntervalSince1970.

